  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.tree.DefaultTreeModel
      • com.cafean.client.ui.navigator.MiniNavigatorTreeModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NavigatorModel, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.swing.event.TreeExpansionListener, javax.swing.event.TreeSelectionListener, javax.swing.tree.TreeModel
    public class MiniNavigatorTreeModel
extends javax.swing.tree.DefaultTreeModel
implements javax.swing.event.TreeExpansionListener, javax.swing.event.TreeSelectionListener, NavigatorModel
    A custom tree model used to respond to treeExpanded and treeCollapsed events from the MiniNavigatorTree
